Paper: hep-th/0001183

Date: 2000-01-27

Title: Type 0 Brane Inflation from Mirage Cosmology

Authors: E.Papantonopoulos and I.Pappa

Comments: 11 pages, latex, one figure

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A15 (2000) 2145-2152

We consider a three-dimensional brane-universe moving in a Type 0 Stringbackground. The motion induces on the brane a cosmological evolution which, forsome range of the parameters, exhibits an inflationary phase.